---
// Partner section
// Background: var(--color-cream-partner) = #FFFCF9
// Two-column layout: left = "Partner With Us" intro, right = "Mutual Benefits" with gold-titled items
---

<section id="partner">
  <div class="section-inner">

    <!-- Top: Partner With Us intro -->
    <div class="partner-intro-block" data-reveal>
      <h2 class="partner-title">
        Partner With Us
        <svg class="paw-decor paw-heading" viewBox="14.245 16.736 171.51 166.528" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false">
          <g>
            <path d="M98.902 88.05c-21.698 0-59.447 52.147-61.533 66.037-2.393 15.935 11.019 29.177 27.133 29.177 10.137 0 30.913-11.779 34.4-11.779 3.367 0 23.912 11.779 34.017 11.779 16.114 0 30.472-13.299 27.725-29.177-2.294-13.264-40.009-66.037-61.742-66.037z" fill="currentColor"></path>
            <path fill="currentColor" d="M91.411 45.161c0 15.699-8.055 28.425-17.991 28.425S55.429 60.86 55.429 45.161s8.055-28.425 17.991-28.425 17.991 12.726 17.991 28.425z"></path>
            <path fill="currentColor" d="M50.227 93.365c0 15.699-8.055 28.425-17.991 28.425s-17.991-12.726-17.991-28.425S22.3 64.94 32.236 64.94s17.991 12.726 17.991 28.425z"></path>
            <path fill="currentColor" d="M144.571 45.161c0 15.699-8.055 28.425-17.991 28.425s-17.991-12.726-17.991-28.425 8.055-28.425 17.991-28.425 17.991 12.726 17.991 28.425z"></path>
            <path fill="currentColor" d="M185.755 89.042c0 15.699-8.055 28.425-17.991 28.425s-17.991-12.726-17.991-28.425 8.055-28.425 17.991-28.425 17.991 12.726 17.991 28.425z"></path>
          </g>
        </svg>
      </h2>
      <img
        src="/images/illus-golden-sitting.png"
        alt=""
        aria-hidden="true"
        class="partner-dog-illus"
      />
      <p class="partner-intro">
        Addressing the complex challenges of canine overpopulation and the global rabies crisis demands more than just passion—it requires powerful partnerships. At Rosie's Heroes, we believe that by uniting with like-minded organizations, corporations, and institutions, we can amplify our impact, innovate solutions, and ultimately create a healthier, safer world for both humans and animals.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Bottom: Mutual Benefits -->
    <div class="partner-benefits-block" data-reveal>
      <h2 class="partner-benefits-heading">
        Mutual <span class="partner-benefits-gold">Benefits</span> of Partnership
      </h2>
      <p class="partner-benefits-sub">
        A partnership with Rosie's Heroes is a mutually beneficial endeavor, offering tangible returns alongside profound social impact:
      </p>

      <div class="partner-benefits-list">

        <div class="partner-benefit" data-reveal="card">
          <h3 class="partner-benefit-title">Measurable Global Impact</h3>
          <p class="partner-benefit-desc">
            Directly contribute to preventing rabies, improving public health, and saving animal lives, with clear reporting on your impact.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="partner-benefit" data-reveal="card">
          <h3 class="partner-benefit-title">Enhanced Brand Alignment &amp; Reputation</h3>
          <p class="partner-benefit-desc">
            Associate your brand with a compassionate, effective, and globally impactful cause, strengthening your public image and corporate values.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="partner-benefit" data-reveal="card">
          <h3 class="partner-benefit-title">Tax Benefits &amp; Recognition</h3>
          <p class="partner-benefit-desc">
            Benefit from tax deductions for charitable contributions and receive recognition across our platforms, events, and reports.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div><!-- /.partner-benefits-list -->
    </div><!-- /.partner-benefits-block -->

  </div><!-- /.section-inner -->
</section>

<style>
  /* --------------------------------------------------------
     PARTNER SECTION
     -------------------------------------------------------- */
  #partner {
    background-color: var(--color-cream-partner); /* #FFFCF9 */
    padding: var(--space-25) 0 var(--space-20);
    position: relative;
  }

  .section-inner {
    max-width: var(--site-width); /* 980px */
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 var(--space-5);
  }

  /* ── Partner With Us intro ──────────────────────────────── */
  .partner-intro-block {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-15); /* 60px */
  }

  .partner-title {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: var(--text-section); /* 38px */
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: var(--lh-tight);
    letter-spacing: var(--ls-tight);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-5);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .paw-heading {
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    color: var(--color-gold);
    vertical-align: middle;
  }

  .partner-dog-illus {
    position: absolute;
    right: 0;
    top: 40px;
    width: 180px;
    height: auto;
    opacity: 0.9;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .partner-intro {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-base); /* 16px */
    line-height: var(--lh-normal);
    color: var(--color-text);
    max-width: 820px;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* ── Mutual Benefits block ──────────────────────────────── */
  .partner-benefits-block {
    /* no extra margin needed */
  }

  .partner-benefits-heading {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: var(--text-section); /* 38px */
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: var(--lh-normal);
    letter-spacing: var(--ls-tight);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-3);
  }

  .partner-benefits-gold {
    color: var(--color-gold); /* #EEBE5A */
  }

  .partner-benefits-sub {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-base); /* 16px */
    line-height: var(--lh-normal);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-10); /* 40px */
    max-width: 820px;
  }

  /* ── Benefits list ──────────────────────────────────────── */
  .partner-benefits-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-8); /* 32px */
  }

  .partner-benefit {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-2); /* 8px */
  }

  .partner-benefit-title {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 17px;
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: var(--lh-normal);
    color: var(--color-gold); /* #EEBE5A */
    margin: 0;
    letter-spacing: var(--ls-snug);
  }

  .partner-benefit-desc {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-base); /* 16px */
    line-height: var(--lh-normal);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 820px;
  }

  /* ── Reveal animations ──────────────────────────────────── */
  [data-reveal]:not([data-reveal="card"]) {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(22px);
    transition: var(--trans-reveal);
  }

  [data-reveal]:not([data-reveal="card"]).visible {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: none;
  }

  [data-reveal="card"] {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(18px) scale(0.97);
    transition: var(--trans-card);
  }

  [data-reveal="card"].visible {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: none;
  }
</style>
